race.comment: COSTA STAR (6) resumes and while she's found the maiden win hard to attain, she's shown glimpses of ability. Expect Yuill to take her back from the draw and be charging hard late. CALL NICK (3) is a lightly raced gelding resuming for the Pearce partnership. Has been readied with a solid trial and is drawn to get all the favours for Faithfull. Can play a major role. ALLA PING (10) has been solid in her first two runs and should be hitting her straps now. Can break through with surprise. ROLL'EMUP (2) is another that finds it tough to get off the mark but has been freshened and gets the blinkers applied for the first time. Watch for sharp improvement.
